beer.beer_description: Brewed in collaboration with the inimitable Bundobust, this is a 5%, juicy pale ale with Nelson Sauvin and Motueka at the forefront, backed up by Simcoe and El Dorado. Bright, tropical, clean and immensely drinkable. This beer marks the first of many collaborative projects with our pals up North!
